UR  - https://www.sciencedirect.com/science/article/pii/0304407678900520
AB  - A model which extends the switching regression models and combines several different limited dependent variable models into a general framework is introduced. Methods to get consistent estimates and asymptotic efficient estimates are derived. Our estimation procedures are then used to study a housing expenditure model which takes into account the simultaneous determination of whether or not to own, and how much to spend.
